                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2" valign="bottom" align="center">
                                <para>Body and trailer stop light relay shorted to ground. Connector 4004 Pin 21 shorted
                                    to ground. Shorted to ground or defective relay.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
